## Move backup file from /tmp to user dir [POST /api/shell/exec]

+ Request (application/json)
        {
            "Cmd":"cp /tmp/backups/latestBackup.tar.gz /home/restoreUser/backups/latestBackup.tar.gz"
        }

+ Response 204 (text/plain)
